Ticket Analysis Sheets

Project Overview:-

This project focuses on analyzing support/service tickets using Microsoft Excel.
The goal is to transform raw ticket data into meaningful insights through data cleaning, processing, and visualization.

1.Features
Data Cleaning & Preprocessing
Ticket Categorization
Status Tracking (Open, Closed, Pending)
Priority Analysis (High, Medium, Low)
Dashboard Visualization
KPI Metrics for decision-making

2.Files Included
Ticket_Analysis_Sheets.xlsx → Main Excel file containing:
Raw Data Sheet
Processed Data
Pivot Tables
Analytics Dashboard

3.Tools Used
Microsoft Excel
Pivot Tables
Charts (Bar, Pie, Line)
Conditional Formatting

4.Dashboard Insights

The dashboard provides:

Total number of tickets
Tickets by priority
Tickets by status
Category-wise distribution
Trend analysis over time

5.How to Use
Download the Excel file
Open in Microsoft Excel
Navigate to the Dashboard sheet
Use filters/slicers to explore data

6.Learning Outcomes
Excel data analysis techniques
Building interactive dashboards
Understanding business metrics
Data visualization best practices
